      "cooked": "<p>We don\u2019t officially support split screen although we try to make it work reasonably well.  <img src=\"https://forums.trainerday.com/images/emoji/twitter/slight_smile.png?v=12\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>\n<p>But crashing in background is not something we have heard of.  It would sound like memory issue.  We will see if we can check the logs and find your error next week.  I will let you know.</p>",
