      "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/forums.trainerday.com/alex/{size}/1331_2.png",
      "created_at": "2024-08-12T07:55:23.426Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Ok, I don\u2019t see any error logs for you specifically (your userid).  I see overall only .5% of our user experience a crash on Android in the last 28 days and 100% of them are on Android 14.  So it seems you are unlucky.</p>\n<p>I see for example 17 hours ago that someone with a Samsung A23 got a crash. that has to do with bluetooth permissions issue and overall most of these crashes seem like bluetooth permissions so this looks like more of an Android 14 issue but I am sure our code could be improved to catch this type of issue.</p>\n<p>Let me know if you can repeat it, if you can you might also try re-installing the app.</p>",
