      "created_at": "2024-08-13T16:11:28.857Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Hi Alex,<br>\nquick reply from during the ride.<br>\nFresh installed app and right after restart:<br>\nNo freezes yet but extreme delay and wrong power/delayed power adjustment. When back in the app: Erg power is back to normal after very fast counting back uf remaining interval time.</p>\n<p>Hope this helps.</p>\n<p>Thanks in advance.</p>",
